		<descript>
			<langdata>eng</langdata>
			<abstract>Non-Attainment Areas: Nitrogen Dioxide is a polygon theme representing areas in the United States that do not meet the National Ambient Air Quality Standard for nitrogen dioxide.</abstract>
			<purpose>To establish the spatial boundaries of each nonattainment and maintenance area.</purpose>
